\title{Interpretivism}

\p{

  A semantic theory associated with [Davidson](davidson). Historically connected to [hermeneutics](phil-016C).
}

\p{What you believe / what your words mean (which have to be determined together) are whatever the best interpretation of your behavior would take them to be (that which best rationalizes your behavior).
}
\p{That's not just the best grip we've got - that's what it \em{is} to mean something.

}
